data.description: Looking for a very spacious home, country style living in quiet area this is your place.  Nice covered porch with 2 car garage and extra uncovered parking.  This house have 2 extra spaces for offices that can be used as extra rooms, offices or a gym.  The family room is huge with a wood burning fireplace, new laminate floors, and double doors for extra classy appeal. Kitchen has newer oak  cabinets with  beautiful ceramic tile backsplash and stainless steel gas stove and dishwasher.  Roof is under 4 years old home has new paint and new flooring throughout.  Plenty of extra space and a private back yard. plus a storage shed in the back yard.
